    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1783360/extras/758e3d44d6be9fefa61a56418352e729.poster.avif?t=1772079387\" width=600 height=160 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1783360/extras/758e3d44d6be9fefa61a56418352e729.webm?t=1772079387\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1783360/extras/758e3d44d6be9fefa61a56418352e729.mp4?t=1772079387\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>住在魔界的魔物“罗伊”和“戈兰”，发现了误入魔界的人类少女“梅格”。<br>性格粗鲁的罗伊，搜寻走失的梅格，和她一起仰望星空，渐渐地同她敞开了心扉。<br>而且，为了将梅格送回她母亲的身边，罗伊决定要前往人类的世界。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1783360/extras/a0c986c2804577f1e99c317e52bf4a56.poster.avif?t=1772079387\" width=600 height=328 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1783360/extras/a0c986c2804577f1e99c317e52bf4a56.webm?t=1772079387\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1783360/extras/a0c986c2804577f1e99c317e52bf4a56.mp4?t=1772079387\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>罗伊非常强健，几乎是无敌的魔物。但是，他必须一边保护梅格一边战斗。<br>有时还需要在战斗中拿出玩具，来安抚梅格不要哭。撑住啊罗伊，打败那些古怪又难缠的怪物们吧。<br>※请注意：如果梅格哭泣，世界就会毁灭（游戏结束）。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1783360/extras/92c07446710541e0813b701f8289892b.poster.avif?t=1772079387\" ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1783360/extras/92c07446710541e0813b701f8289892b.mp4?t=1772079387\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>在旅途中，魔界中形形色色的魔物们，会将故事点缀得更加欢乐而丰满。<br>好搭档“戈兰”、统领魔界的“评议会”巨头们、住在魔界的人类“保尔”……<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1783360/extras/dae0302a63f5ae52eb28373fb9d7f2e9.poster.avif?t=1772079387\" width=600 height=126 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1783360/extras/dae0302a63f5ae52eb28373fb9d7f2e9.webm?t=1772079387\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1783360/extras/dae0302a63f5ae52eb28373fb9d7f2e9.mp4?t=1772079387\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>不让梅格伤心落泪，将她安全送到地上的世界——你，做得到吧？",
